title: Graphic Design, ""On the Beach, Two are Company, Three are None"", August 17, 1872
medium: Wood engraving printed in black ink on paper
inscribed: Caption: "On the Beach-Two are Company, Three are None. - Drawn by Winslow Homer."
description: Horizontal view of a woman in foreground, looking over her shoulder towards man and woman on a beached dory, with the ocean visible in the background.

Graphic Design, ""On the Beach, Two are Company, Three are None"", August 17, 1872.
August 17, 1872. Wood engraving printed in black ink on paper. Gift of Edith Wetmore. 1936-30-7.
